<section id="data" class="pt-8 border-t border-border">
  <h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider">How data is collected</h2>
  <div class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <p class="m-0">
        Data comes from a curated list of <strong class="text-foreground">5,000 high-impact npm packages</strong> from <a href="https://github.com/wooorm/npm-high-impact" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:no-underline">npm-high-impact</a>. Each package's latest version is fetched from the npm registry and classified by inspecting its <code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted">package.json</code>
      </p>
      <p class="m-0">
        Classification looks at <code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted">type</code>, <code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted">exports</code>, <code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted">module</code>, <code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted">main</code>, and file extensions (<code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted">.mjs</code> / <code class="text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-muted">.cjs</code>). Known spam and placeholder packages are excluded.
      </p>
      <p class="m-0">
        The crawl runs <strong class="text-foreground">weekly on Mondays at 06:00 UTC</strong> via GitHub Actions. Historical data is bootstrapped from <a href="https://github.com/wooorm/npm-esm-vs-cjs" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:no-underline">npm-esm-vs-cjs</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-6 border-t border-border">
      <h3 class="m-0 mb-3 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider">Data sources & credits</h3>
      <ul class="m-0 list-none flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/wooorm/npm-high-impact" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:no-underline">npm-high-impact</a> — curated package list</li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/wooorm/npm-esm-vs-cjs" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:no-underline">npm-esm-vs-cjs</a> — historical classification data</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:no-underline">npm registry</a> — package metadata</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
